# 定义一个函数来执行灰色关联分析，其中每个化学成分轮流作为参考序列，并将结果可视化
def all_chemicals_grey_correlation_analysis(data):
    chemicals = data.columns.drop(['类型', '表面风化', '文物采样点'])
    
    # 存储所有关联度结果
    all_correlation_results = {chemical: {} for chemical in chemicals}
    
    for group_name, group_data in data.groupby('类型'):
        group_data.drop(columns=['类型', '表面风化', '文物采样点'], inplace=True)
        
        # 针对每个化学成分执行灰色关联分析
        for chemical in chemicals:
            reference_sequence = group_data[chemical]
            correlation_matrix = group_data.apply(lambda x: grey_correlation(reference_sequence, x))
            all_correlation_results[chemical][group_name] = correlation_matrix
    
    return all_correlation_results

# 执行灰色关联分析
all_correlation_results = all_chemicals_grey_correlation_analysis(data)

# 可视化结果
for chemical, correlation_result in all_correlation_results.items():
    for group_name, result in correlation_result.items():
        plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))
        result.plot(kind='bar')
        plt.title(f"{group_name} - Grey Correlation with {chemical}")
        plt.ylabel("Correlation Degree")
        plt.show()

# 创建一个空的DataFrame列表，用于保存灰色关联度统计数据
correlation_summary_list = []

# 遍历每个类别，计算每个化学成分作为母序列的灰色关联度
for group_name, group_data in grouped_data:
    group_data.drop(columns=['类型', '表面风化', '文物采样点'], inplace=True)
    for col in group_data.columns:
        reference_sequence = group_data[col]
        correlation_values = group_data.apply(lambda x: grey_correlation(reference_sequence, x))
        correlation_matrix = pd.DataFrame({'化学成分': group_data.columns, '关联度': correlation_values})
        correlation_matrix['参考化学成分'] = col
        correlation_matrix['类别'] = group_name
        correlation_summary_list.append(correlation_matrix)

# 使用 pandas.concat 连接 DataFrame 列表
correlation_summary = pd.concat(correlation_summary_list, ignore_index=True)

# 分别绘制两个类别的折线图
for category in correlation_summary['类别'].unique():
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    category_data = correlation_summary[correlation_summary['类别'] == category]
    for reference_chemical in category_data['参考化学成分'].unique():
        reference_data = category_data[category_data['参考化学成分'] == reference_chemical]
        plt.plot(reference_data['关联度'].values, label=reference_chemical)
    plt.title(f"灰色关联度折线图 - 类别: {category}")
    plt.xlabel('化学成分')
    plt.ylabel('灰色关联度')
    plt.xticks(ticks=range(len(group_data.columns)), labels=group_data.columns, rotation=90)
    plt.legend()
    plt.show()

def grey_correlation_analysis(data):
    reference_sequence = data['SiO2']
    correlation_matrix = data.apply(lambda x: grey_correlation(reference_sequence, x))
    return correlation_matrix

# 定义灰色关联度计算函数
def grey_correlation(reference_sequence, comparison_sequence, xi=0.5):
    delta_x0 = abs(reference_sequence - comparison_sequence)
    min_delta_x0 = delta_x0.min()
    max_delta_x0 = delta_x0.max()
    correlation_degree = (min_delta_x0 + xi * max_delta_x0) / (delta_x0 + xi * max_delta_x0)
    return correlation_degree.mean()

# 重新执行灰色关联分析
correlation_results = {}
for group_name, group_data in grouped_data:
    group_data.drop(columns=['类型', '表面风化', '文物采样点'], inplace=True)
    correlation_results[group_name] = grey_correlation_analysis(group_data)


# 将数据按类型分组

for group_name, group_data in grouped_data:
    group_data.drop(columns=['类型', '表面风化', '文物采样点'], inplace=True)
    correlation_results[group_name] = grey_correlation_analysis(group_data)
